Class GuiConfigEntries.ListEntryBase

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.minecraftforge.fml.client.config.GuiConfigEntries.ListEntryBase
  • All Implemented Interfaces:

    Direct Known Subclasses:
    GuiConfigEntries.ButtonEntry, GuiConfigEntries.CategoryEntry, GuiConfigEntries.StringEntry

    GuiConfigEntries

    public abstract static class GuiConfigEntries.ListEntryBase
extends java.lang.Object
implements GuiConfigEntries.IConfigEntry
    ListEntryBase Provides a base entry for others to extend. Handles drawing the prop label (if drawLabel == true) and the Undo/Default buttons.
